## Agent Execution Protocol

> **Read this first.** Follow this loop autonomously — do not wait for the user to say "what's next".

```
1. bd ready                          # find the next available task for this spec
2. If nothing ready → bd blocked     # check for blockers; surface to user if unresolvable
3. bd update <id> --claim            # claim the task
4. Read the issue description fully before writing any code
5. Implement the task
6. npm test                          # MUST pass before closing — fix failures first
7. npm run lint                      # MUST pass before closing — fix errors first
8. bd close <id>                     # close the completed task
9. Go to step 1
```

When `bd ready` returns nothing, run the **Land the Plane Checklist** in PLAN.md.

